title: WWE 2K16 season pass grants access to all DLC offerings
text: Thursday, Oct 8 2015, 02:51   Twitter Share on Google+ WWE 2K16 fans may want to invest in the season pass for the upcoming wrestling video game.Priced at $24.99 (Â£16), the season pass grants access to all of the title's downloadable content as soon as they become available.DLC offerings include the 'Future Stars' pack, which will add Samoa Joe, Diego, Fernando, Blake and Murphy to the WWE 2K16 roster.Meanwhile, a new 'Moves Pack' and Accelerator are designed to help players get their preferred Superstars or Divas to reach their virtual peak. WWE 2K16 is set to launch on October 27 in North America and on October 30 internationally for PS4, Xbox One, PS3 and Xbox 360.
